CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 17, reads: "McDonald, coached by Edward Lee, succeeded Central Baptist as the champions of the Community Church League this year. The League was sponsored by the Centre Avenue YMCA.  Members of the championship team are, left to right: Edward Lee, coach; John Randolph, Art Catlin, Zeke Walser, Luther Turner, Clarence Lewis and Warren Thomas."
TitMainTitle: Basketball team wearing "BFH" jerseys, from left: coach Edward Lee, John Randolph, Art Catlin, Zeke Walser, Luther Turner, Clarence Lewis, and Warren Thomas, in Centre Avenue YMCA gymnasium
